      Modifier and Type Interface Description
      interface  IInstallCmdData
      This is the well-known DataPacketData type that contains the install new command command (command that has a new a command), which is an ADataPacketAlgoCmd, that notifies its receiver that it has a command for an originally unknown type for the sender.
      interface  IJoinData
      This is the well-known DataPacketData type that contains the join chatroom command, which is an ADataPacketAlgoCmd, that notifies its receiver that it wants to join a chatroom.
      interface  ILeaveData
      This is the well-known DataPacketData type that contains the leave chatroom command, which is an ADataPacketAlgoCmd, that notifies its receiver that it wants to leave a chatroom.
      interface  IRequestCmdData
      This is the well-known DataPacketData type that contains the request new command command (command that gets a command), which is an ADataPacketAlgoCmd, that notifies its receiver that it needs a command for some unknown type.
      interface  ITxtData
      This is the well-known DataPacketData type that contains the send text chatroom command, which is an ADataPacketAlgoCmd, that sends a text message to its receiver.

      This is the well-known status error message that is sent when a request message is received asking for a well-known message type.

    • Uses of IDataPacketData in common.message.synchronization

      Subinterfaces of IDataPacketData in common.message.synchronization 
      Modifier and Type Interface Description
      interface  IUpdateMemberListAddData
      This is the well-known DataPacketData type that contains a list of member stubs, meant to update a member's IGroup's member list by adding these members if not already present.
      interface  IUpdateMemberListData
      This is the well-known DataPacketData type that contains the request to update a member's local instance of a group's member list with a list of members in order to ensure a fully connected P2P graph network.
      interface  IUpdateMemberListRemoveData
      This is the well-known DataPacketData type that contains a list of member stubs and is meant to update a member's local instance of a group's member list by removing these members from their list, if present.
